    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Meditation against Wits\nType: Normal\nQi: 7\n\nYou enter calmly into meditation and project your thoughts into the minds of others, awakening images that seem real to them. Make a Meditation Roll against the Wits of up to 1 Target per rank of Qi. If you succeed then you can play with their senses, creating false images in their minds that feel real. This can extend to touch, taste, sound etc. The illusion can be large, can involve multiple senses but must be focused on a particular idea (such as a forest). The illusion lasts for as long as you Meditate. IMMORTAL",
